---

<SectionContainer>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
    <span
      class="before:-z-1 relative z-10 mb-4 inline-block text-3xl font-bold before:absolute before:bottom-0 before:left-0 before:-z-10 before:block before:h-[12px] before:w-full before:skew-x-[25deg] before:bg-secondary xs:text-4xl"
      >Still not sure?</span
    >
    <p class="max-w-prose text-balance text-neutral-content">
      Take our short quiz to find out which of our award winning toys is best
      for you!
    </p>
    <a
      href="https://mygiddi.com/tools/perfect-product-finder/quiz"
      target="_blank"
      class="btn btn-outline btn-primary btn-accent mt-8">take quiz</a
    >
